result:
<a-modal
  title="技能管理"
  style="top: 40px;"
  :width="600"
  :afterClose="afterClose"
  :destroyOnClose="true"
  v-model="visible"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
>
  <a-select
    mode="multiple"
    style="width: 80%"
    @change="handleChange"     
    placeholder="添加技能"
  >
    <a-select-option v-for="(i,index) in skillList" :key="index" :disabled="i.isDel?true:false">{{ i.title }}</a-select-option>
  </a-select>
</a-modal>
